out somewhere — even if into nonexistence. 'Let's go, let's go,' cried someone and disappeared with a bang. He remained alone. His vision became darker and darker and in relation to every vague object in the hall he stood in check. He had to escape; he moved, the whole of his fat body shaking, and was completely unable to imagine what people did in order to get out of a room — and yet there should be a simple method — abruptly a black shade with a white breast began to hover about him, off